event: response.output_text.done
data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_0cd27d1b0d94de9e016a04a31230048197b3ef185c2c24f1a4","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":489,"text":"Let t be hours after 3:00 pm when they meet (t ≥ 1). The distances they travel add to 470 km:\n80t + 100(t − 1) = 470\n180t − 100 = 470 → 180t = 570 → t = 570/180 = 19/6 = 3 1/6 h = 3 h 10 min.\n\nThey meet at 3:00 + 3:10 = 6:10 pm.\n\nDistance from Paris = 80t = 80 × 19/6 = 760/3 ≈ 253.33 km (253 km 333 m)."}

